head.title: Treasury to Auction Only Bills This Week

hedline.hl1: Treasury to Auction Only Bills This Week

block.p: This week's Treasury financings are limited to the regular weekly auction today of new three- and six-month bills.
By late in the day Friday, the interest rate of a three-month bill was 3.64 percent; a six-month bill was at 3.76 percent.
